{"tid":18675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打擊走資! 澳門擬收緊旅客攜帶現金申報","createTime":"2016-12-02T11:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T10:09:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3c9ad4b43c00150c1a8cdf384bda8ea6145065","tid":18675,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"澳門博彩股全線下跌 澳門擬收緊旅客攜帶現金申報制度 <br />\n2/12/2016 10:22 <br />\n<br />\n澳門博彩股全線下跌, 銀河娛樂最新報36元, 跌1.5元, 跌幅百分之4; 金沙中國報36.6元, 跌1.4元, 跌幅百分之3.7; 澳博報6.19元, 跌0.15元, 跌幅百分之2.3; 美高梅中國報16.74元, 跌0.18元, 跌幅百分之1; 永利澳門報13.38元, 跌0.4元, 跌幅百分之2.9; 新濠國際報12.16元, 跌0.44元, 跌幅百分之3.5. <br />\n<br />\n澳門電台昨日報導, 澳門政府計劃要求, 旅客入境攜帶超過總值12萬澳門元現金, 或無記名可轉讓票據入境時必須申報, 否則屬於行政違法, 罰款最多50萬澳門元, 相關法律草案將提交立法會審議. <br />\n<br />\n另外, 澳門十一月的博彩收入為188億澳門元, 按年上升百分之14, 是連續第四個月錄得按年升幅, 並且是超過兩年半以來, 最大單月升幅. <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20161202102236&amp;page=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FSearchText%3D%26NewsId%3D20161202102236%26page%3D0&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=0559ee27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20161202102236&amp;page=0</a>"},{"pid":"d4fa4462d52d628b8063df84533b4eb5b7542ff5","tid":18675,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2902b64a59869cdcaf4f1b288c5b116db2b235","tid":18675,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"防洗黑錢 ?"},{"pid":"266c140350635e449c04f63ce073680e9121b0bb","tid":18675,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"邊個會申報呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98729e415ea627763e5b3522d260fdef88b4b8a","tid":18675,"uid"